Trinity::

She got up and walked over to Zeni. "I'm sorry. I didn't mean to 
pester you like that. I was only trying to help."  She looked up at 
Gramps and then to Zeni. "Well, even if you don't like my mode, can I 
still help you find the one that you want Zeni?" she smiled at him.

> Zeni: No, I'm not afraid of you.
> 
> He watched Trinity walk away and sit by the ship with a pouty face.
> 
> Zeni: But I can take a beast mode that is Trinity's idea.
> 
> Perplex: Your really sweet, Zeni, nice to Trinity like that, maybe 
we should
> all do that, I mean, I can't find anything that would suit me, and 
Gramps,
> admit it, your having trouble.
